	* typemanager.cs.cs (GetInterfaces): Don't recreate 0-sized arrays.

2006-03-15  Marek Safar  <marek.safar@seznam.cz>

	* class.cs (FieldMember.Emit): ParentContainer is real parent for partial
	classes.

