	Fix #75636.
	* expression.cs (Invocation.OverloadResolve): Replace reflected
	override methods with their base virtual methods, rather than
	skipping over them.
	* typemanager.cs (TypeManager.GetOverride): New.

2006-01-05  Jb Evain  <jbevain@gmail.com>

