2005-07-05  Marek Safar  <marek.safar@seznam.cz>
 
 	The big error and warning messages review.
 	
 	* anonymous.cs,
 	* assign.cs,
 	* attribute.cs,
 	* class.cs,
 	* codegen.cs,
 	* convert.cs,
 	* cs-parser.jay,
