	* expression.cs (Argument.GetParameterModifier): Turned to property.
	(Invocation.Error_InvalidArguments): Add more descriptive errors.
	
	* parameter.cs (Parameter.GetModifierSignature): Translates modifier to
	its C# equivalent.
	
