	* class.cs (EmitFieldInitializers): Use FieldExpr in initializer.
	
	* ecore.cs (FieldExpr): Add a new ctor with in_initializer.
	(FieldExpr.DoResolve): Obsolete members are ignored for field
	initializers.
	
